Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:07.51,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你

Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:19.79,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしよう　あなたに出逢うまでの私　忘れちゃったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:23.94,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,風は頬を撫でる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:26.80,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ララバイ　オブ　バードランド♪　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:30.95,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,坂道蹴りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.68,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,頼りない影は伸びる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:39.76,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,終わらない夏休みみたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:45.59,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,プールに忍び込んでる気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:51.19,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　服のまま泳ごうよ   跳ねる　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:54.33,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,衝撃的誘惑スパイラル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.62,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,この胸を突き刺すビートはストレンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:02.50,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,それはパッと燃えて消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.31,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,散々な日々も上等　ドレスアップ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:09.58,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,スウィングしてる　ハイなスピード　サラウンド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.18,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,それは何ていうダンス？止まらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:19.79,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,行かないで　耳に絡みついてもう離れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:27.35,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,メロディは　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:31.89,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,恋みたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:19.79,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}自從和你相遇 我已忘了原來的那個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:23.94,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}風輕撫著臉頰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:26.80,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}猶如小鳥天堂的安眠曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:30.95,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}踢著坡道走著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.68,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}孤單的影子慢慢伸長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:39.76,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仿佛這個暑假永遠無法結束一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:45.59,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有種躲進了游泳池的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:51.19,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呐~ 就這麼穿著衣服游吧 瘋起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:54.33,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}衝擊性的誘惑螺旋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.62,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}撞擊胸膛的節奏是如此奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:02.50,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那是瞬間燃起又消逝的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.31,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}狼狽不堪的日子來得正好 盛裝打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:09.58,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}搖擺起來 用歡快的律動 填滿四周
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.18,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這究竟是什麼舞步？ 為何無法停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:19.79,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請不要離去 這縈繞於耳畔的旋律已使我無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:27.35,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:31.89,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}猶如熱戀般


Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:31.89,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.93,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,姓是深堀　名字是百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.31,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,２年紀６班　學號是２２號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.82,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,是高一個年級的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.76,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,初中一年級時從東京轉學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.52,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,愛好是油畫和玩長刀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.19,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,生日２月１０日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:15.07,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,以上 僅供參考
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.45,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,在說啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.87,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.45,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這不是變硬了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.84,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想到她 胸口就感覺被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:28.14,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,連飯也咽不下去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.04,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.02,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這完全是得了相思病了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.74,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,這算是 戀愛？　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:40.13,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是至今還沒有戀愛過吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.03,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.02,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:48.21,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果這傢伙能夠對那個人著迷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:52.66,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我和律醬之間不是沒有人會來插一腳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:58.53,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 今天放學後 爵士暫停 進行作戰會議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.78,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 要在我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.22,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,律醬家的地下室 不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:09.48,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,對 你在自己家裡也比較安心不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.14,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:16.62,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那個地下室的話  也難保不被律醬聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.65,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,就是這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.48,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這兒不是律醬的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:24.45,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,我家和律醬家是連在一棟的長屋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.83,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,喂 媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.16,ch-default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.81,ch-default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你回來啦 今天很早嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.15,ch-default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,過來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.19,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下 媽媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.46,ch-default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 哥哥回來嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:37.89,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.21,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,你愣在那兒幹啥 進來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.81,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,媽 這傢伙就是公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.93,ch-default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.27,ch-default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎一直承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.32,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.63,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣 吃吧 公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.41,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,你不是剛才沒有食欲的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:06.95,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜是另當別論
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.87,ch-default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎特別喜歡吃西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:14.48,ch-default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,最近少見的說飯吃不下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:18.38,ch-default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,我想西瓜的話就能吃得下 就特地先冰了下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.60,ch-default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.79,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,咋了 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.67,ch-default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,有個很奇怪的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:25.59,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.66,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,大不大？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.59,ch-default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:31.12,ch-default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  西瓜的種子種下去 會長出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.65,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就種種看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.85,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:36.55,ch-default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,飛掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.86,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了 別哭了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.11,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,團體交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:47.53,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,對 包括我和律醬 4個人一起出門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.27,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就要2個人獨處會起戒心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.12,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.66,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,去邀請百合香小姐的 當然是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.64,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不是你邀請的話就沒意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.72,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我辦不到 絕對辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.13,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:05.84,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.01,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.16,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,薩拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.34,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,我的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.20,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.35,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？　薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.85,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,心情不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:20.03,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,可愛吧 正式名字是 薩拉 伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.49,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,鴿子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.22,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.74,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,今天還真是暴躁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.96,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,是在嫉妒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.74,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一直在聊別的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.37,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒？　我這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.67,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,莫名變得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.89,ch-default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.96,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.34,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.12,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.45,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 哪有就這麼跑回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.86,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.77,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,小抄  小抄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.02,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,噢 噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.53,ch-default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.35,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.08,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,叫住你不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:19.25,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,本周的休息日有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:26.26,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,籍此機會 促進 我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.46,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,友誼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:30.23,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,為了加深友誼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.23,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.48,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,公子哥 公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.08,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  她說去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.90,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,是去幽會岩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.81,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,是不是帶著便當去比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:48.59,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那個 的確呢 飯團之類 比較輕量的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.59,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就做點什麼帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:54.07,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 為了避免誤會 我還是問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.58,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,約我的是你們之中哪一個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.93,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:04.96,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 說無論如何也要約你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.29,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.47,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:09.56,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.25,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,那 就期待著那天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:14.26,ch-default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,約會你ok了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.36,ch-default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.68,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨蛋 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:21.84,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易感覺不錯了 一下子就被你搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:25.36,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要那樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.69,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,快把時間倒回來 公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.82,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼有這能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.57,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.97,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了來了 薫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.03,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,喂 臉上的傷是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.60,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎打架不是家常便飯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.83,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 薫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:50.04,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,等下 律醬 其實今天還要來一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.13,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.43,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.33,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,做便當花了些工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.43,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,應該是海邊被不良少年糾纏的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.06,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.28,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,你記得她？　其實今天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.43,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.54,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,是戴眼鏡的那個男生約我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.40,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你沒事吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.86,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,被薫同學約？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.74,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.40,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你在幹嘛啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:19.32,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,新來的加入打擾你們 沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.58,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.24,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒有的事 人多點更開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.08,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.66,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來是薫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.51,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,美人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.81,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學原來是外貌協會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.30,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.09,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼 就是覺得帽子真是時髦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.60,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.82,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我戴了也只會被人說是地瓜妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.07,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.54,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,稍微失禮下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.08,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,律醬 什麼時候髮型變了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.68,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,百合香前輩幫我弄的  怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:09.08,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯呢 非常可愛噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:20.09,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 律子醬家裡是開唱片行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.10,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 百合香前輩 你喜歡爵士音樂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:30.09,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人 是爵士搭檔 每天都在練習噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.58,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,演奏爵士？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:36.59,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 薫同學彈鋼琴 千太郎是鼓手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:40.18,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  要說聽爵士的 我周圍倒是有幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.24,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,但是演奏爵士的還是頭一次遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.88,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我有兩個哥哥都是爵士愛好者  我也不時會聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:49.74,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥們都是皺著眉頭聽一些很高深的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.30,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是喜歡那種對身體有衝擊力的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.71,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,對 對啊對啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.13,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我也想聽聽你敲鼓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:03.64,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行 還很差勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:08.01,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,不在別人面前演奏的話是不會有長進的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:09.25,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,讓我聽聽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.09,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這真是 意外的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.06,ch-default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:17.71,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 好像被樹枝擦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:28.02,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 那傢伙 挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.67,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,一起登上那個岩石的情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.80,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,據說會終成眷屬噢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.09,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,對女人來說 太難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.80,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,公子哥 一起爬上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.18,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:46.19,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,哎呦 這我可不能當作沒聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.18,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,這點不算什麼 爬給你們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.37,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,誰要一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.61,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.11,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:03.03,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個 牌子上寫著禁止進入 有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:07.89,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,啊 遺憾 還想上去欣賞一下那裡的風景的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.02,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,吃得太急了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.47,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人 好像相當合得來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.99,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學 你可以把這個吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.06,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.18,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,去摘花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.48,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,是上廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.75,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是大啊 這個飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.58,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.09,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,是我傷害了律醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.08,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,通過如此殘忍的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.10,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我把最重要的女孩弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:19.11,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,安慰她那寂寞的肩膀的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.68,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.91,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 薫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.27,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:37.98,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.77,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,你稍微過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.07,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,這個 這塊手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:48.67,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,百合香前輩 說是作為手巾的賠禮 給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.31,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,好像有種好聞的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.56,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.83,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.04,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:10.03,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓你撿起這手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.91,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.34,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,手帕的話 還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.62,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.44,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.97,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼意思 你明白點說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.84,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.96,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,你只要有了這個手帕 就滿足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:34.50,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,一個人去好好聞手帕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.08,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這是想要打架？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.23,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:46.40,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎　放開薫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.41,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.77,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,不要動粗 跟薫同學道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.29,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.09,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管 這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.15,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,等等　千太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.42,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,這個不能忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.25,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的手帕 不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:14.85,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.81,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎　現在這時候已經像傻子一樣在敲鼓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.12,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,「公子哥個笨蛋～！」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.13,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,和好還是要趁早噢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.09,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,過來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.19,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:35.58,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,在薫同學轉學過來之前 千太郎總是一個人在練習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:40.04,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,窩在地下室裡  誰也無法靠近的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.83,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,那地下室的氣氛 連我也不敢進去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:47.57,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,但是薫同學來了以後 那樣的氣氛就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:51.82,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,一定是找到了一起玩爵士的夥伴  高興著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:57.85,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學 今天吵架的原因 我來猜一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:02.56,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學 你喜歡百合香前輩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.86,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,因為千太郎炫耀那個手帕　不開心了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.88,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:14.12,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我也想長成那個樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.90,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.04,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,律醬也 也是非常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.47,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,有魅力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.30,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學真是的 謝謝你的鼓勵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.59,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.53,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼鼓勵呢 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.93,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.09,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.82,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,喂 律醬　開門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.74,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,這是在鬧什麼　律子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.15,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,強迫治療法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:54.53,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裡 可不是因為找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.62,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:05.14,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:13.32,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 對喜歡的女孩子的心情  應該是和我同樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.56,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要隨便就跟我合奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.06,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.48,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,誰跟你合奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.37,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,又跟上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.13,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.21,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,祭典用爵士樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:59.08,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 一笑就沒法彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:36.20,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,下次 專門為律醬彈一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:42.35,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,然後 試著把心聲告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.01,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.97,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.37,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 不要那麼拘束嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:07.04,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 在 在幹嗎啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:15.23,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,律醬 心裡一定在想著他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:20.43,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在那傢伙卻...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.60,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那個 律醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.64,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我有曲子想讓你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:35.22,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,其實是想再多練習下的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.81,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷特別訓練的那支曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.91,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,現在 無論如何 也想讓你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.83,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,請降臨吧 bill evans大師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.29,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,是叫「有一天王子會出現」的曲子噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.88,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學 就是這個王子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:20.93,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:23.87,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,為了彈給百合香前輩聽而練習的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:27.10,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,這是 預備練習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:28.97,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.82,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這是正式的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.61,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的人 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.82,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不用現在馬上就回復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.87,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,只是這裡有一個很喜歡的你的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.79,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,只是想告訴你這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.32,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,律醬的眼裡只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:05.48,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在牽掛的也是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.63,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,現在即使這樣也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:14.91,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,能夠這樣的喜歡上一個人 這是你教給我的





Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:27.61,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,あの坂道で君を待っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:35.71,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,放課後の約束に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:40.59,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,遠く滲む「さようなら」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:50.34,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,弱くて歪ですぐに壊れそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:55.02,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,あの頃の僕にね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:22:03.03,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,小さいな翼を　君がくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:08.45,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,夕闇が染み入った空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:14.22,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,微かな光 探している
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:22.27,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,君が好きだと　好きだと言えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:34.56,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,教科書の隅に書いた手紙は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:39.87,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:43.13,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,届かずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:48.06,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,あの日のまま
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:27.61,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在那坡道上  等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:35.71,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}隨著放學後的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:40.59,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}而漸聲遠去的道別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:50.34,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}弱小而執拗  脆弱而容易受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:55.02,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那個時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:22:03.03,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}得到了你給予的小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:08.45,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在逐漸浸染黃昏的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:14.22,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}尋找微弱的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:22.27,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}如果那時能夠說出喜歡你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:34.56,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}悄悄在教科書的一角寫下的書信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:39.87,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}卻一如當初
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:43.13,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}無論到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:48.06,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}都無法傳達
